#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc112
msgctxt "pli-tv-kd4:13.1.120"
msgid "Na, bhikkhave, tadahu pavāraṇāya sabhikkhukā āvāsā sabhikkhuko āvāso gantabbo, yatthassu bhikkhū nānāsaṃvāsakā, aññatra saṃghena, aññatra antarāyā."
